ts/peso-pluma">Peso Pluma</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/j-balvin">J Balvin</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/khruangbin">Khruangbin</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jhene-aiko">Jhené Aiko</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lil-uzi-vert">Lil Uzi Vert</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/justice">Justice</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/deftones">Deftones</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sublime">Sublime</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jungle">Jungle</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dom-dolla">Dom Dolla</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bleachers">Bleachers</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/peggy-gou">Peggy Gou</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/le-sserafim">LE SSERAFIM</a>等。</p><p> Coachella 音乐节的第一个周末就受到了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coachellas-main-stage-plagued-by-sound-issues-throughout-day-one-3617209">无数声音问题的困扰</a>，导致 Lana Del Rey 等艺术家的声音几乎听不见，而 Grimes <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/grimes-dj-set-at-coachella-mired-by-technical-difficulties-social-media-reacts-3617464">在 DJ 表演中遇到了大量的技术问题，让她沮丧地尖叫起来</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3617875" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3617875" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3617875" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/blur-coachella-2024.jpg" alt="Blur 的达蒙·阿尔本" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/blur-coachella-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/blur-coachella-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/blur-coachella-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/blur-coachella-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/blur-coachella-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/blur-coachella-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" siz